    &gt;
        &lt;sup style=&quot;color: var(--primary-color)&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;sup&gt; You could *maybe* make it deterministic by using the starting location of the &quot;operation&quot; as an ordering for the change? I&#x27;m not entirely sure.
